# 1
# Weak form
# Adapted from a:114
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: pronouns
n boɔro la koɔraa
n         boɔ-ro    la   koɔraa
1s.NOM.WK love-IPFV FACT farmer
'I love a farmer'

# 2
# Strong form
# Adapted from a:114
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: pronouns
maa boɔro la koɔraa
maa        boɔ-ro    la   koɔraa
1s.NOM.STR love-IPFV FACT farmer
'I, for one, love a farmer'

